  "text": "HomeEditors' PicksWash it all away, and feel both fancy and cozy while doing it.Loopha Oud + Amber Hand + Body Wash, $13.86, available herePhoto: Courtesy of LoophaEditors' Picks are the Fashionista team's true (#notspon) fashion and beauty obsessions, handpicked by professionals who see it all. Any beauty product you see here has been vetted and tested by the editor recommending it.This fall, Deciem — the parent company behind brands like The Ordinary and Niod – (re)launched Loopha, a body-care brand that focuses on elevated scents and quality skin-care ingredients. Of the product offerings, a standout for me is the Oud + Amber Hand + Body Wash, which I've been using as a bathroom hand soap for the last few weeks. It's a gorgeous way to wash it all away, and feel both fancy and cozy while doing it.As the product name suggests, the scent comprises notes of wood and amber, as well as a subtle hint of bergamot and tonka bean. The result is a luxurious, earthy, comforting aroma that lingers pleasantly on skin without being too overpowering.Scroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesThe formula itself is lovely, too: It relies on a gentle, non-drying blend of surfactants to create a soft lather, and is also spiked with jojoba esters, glycerin and vitamin E to moisturize and protect skin.It's a multi-purpose product that, at $18, rivals any other fancy scented body wash or hand soap on the market, many of which surpass the $30 or even $50 price tag. Even better: For the month of November, it's on sale: A 23% discount is automatically applied at checkout, bringing the product's grand total to $13.86. So if you, too, want to smell like a rich-person blend of wood and amber — without requiring a rich person budget — now is your moment.Loopha Oud + Amber Hand + Body Wash, $18 $13.86, available herePlease note: This product was gifted. Occasionally, we use affiliate links on our site. In no way do either affect our editorial decision-making.Tune into the Fashionista Network to join the conversation with fashion and beauty industry leaders. Sign up here.Subscribe to Our Newsletter",
