ionista.com/tag/body-wash\"\u003ebody wash\u003c/a\u003e or hand soap on the market, many of which surpass the $30 or even $50 price tag. Even better: For the month of November, it\u0026#39;s on sale: A 23% discount is automatically applied at checkout, bringing the product\u0026#39;s grand total to $13.86. So if you, too, want to smell like a rich-person blend of wood and amber — without requiring a rich person budget — now is your moment.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLoopha Oud + Amber Hand + Body Wash, \u003cs\u003e$18\u003c/s\u003e $13.86,\u003ca href=\"https://loopha.com/en-us/oud-amber-hand-body-wash-100703.html\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e available here\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eP\u003c/em\u003e\u003cem\u003elease note: This product was gifted. Occasionally, we use affiliate links on our site. In no way do either affect our editorial decision-making.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/S522\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTune into the Fashionista Network to join the conversation with fashion and beauty industry leaders. Sign up here.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phxbrandengagement-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-7\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eSubscribe to Our Newsletter\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phxlisthub-3\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-8\"\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/cs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good/MTQ1NTQ5OTY2NzI5ODE1NjA3/mtqwndi3ntcznze1oda1njgw-1.svg\" alt=\"Related Stories\"/\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cphoenix-hub data-group-si